{"header":{"word":"עֵ֫שֶׂב","entry":7468,"letter":"ע","strongs":6212,"page":793},"definitions":[{"title":"Def","body":" &#134; [[עֵ֫שֶׂב]] ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"n.m.","body":":Ge 1:11 herb, herbage;&#8212;&#180;[[ע]] abs. De 11:15 +; cstr. Ge 2:5 +; sf. [[עֶשְׂבָּם]] Is 42:15; pl. cstr. [[עִשְּׂבוֹת]] (d. f. dirim.) Pr 27:25; &#8212;herb, herbage, in oldest use oft. gen. (therefore incl. grass [[[דֶּשֶׁא]]]): [[הַשָּׂדֶה]] &#180;[[ע]] Ex 9:22 (E), Ge 2:5 (+ [[שִׂיחַ]]) Ex 9:25 (+ [[עֵץ]]), Ex 10:15 (+ id; all J) Am 7:2, so [[הָאָרֶץ]] &#180;[[ע]] Ex 10:12 (E), + [[פְּרִי הָעֵץ]] v:Ex 10:15 (J), whence Ps 105:35; appar. gen. also in [[הארץ]] &#180;[[ע]] Job 5:25, Ps 72:16, &#180;[[ע]] alone Ps 92:8; [[כָּל־הַשָּׂדֶה]] &#180;[[ע]] Je 12:14, &#180;[[ע]] alone De 32:2 (&#8214;[[דֶּשֶׁא]]), Is 42:15, Ps 102:5, Ps 102:12, and De 29:22, Mic 5:6, Pr 19:12; hence &#180;[[ע]] as food for cattle De 11:15, Ps 106:20 cf. Je 14:6, Zec 10:1; [[עִשְּׂבוֹת הָרִים]] Pr 27:25 (&#8214;[[דֶּשֶׁא]], [[חָחִיר]]); but as human food (hence excluding [[דֶּשֶׁא]]) [[הַשָּׂדֶה]] &#180;[[ע]] Ge 3:18 (J); esp. P Ge 1:29 (+ [[עֶץ]]), &#180;[[יֶרֶק ע]] v:Ge 1:30, Ge 9:3, hence &#180;[[ע]] Ps 104:14 (&#8214;[[חָחִיר]] for cattle); &#180;[[ע]] disting. fr. [[דֶּשֶׁא]], [[עֵץ]] also Ge 1:11, Ge 1:12, [[שָׂדֶה]] &#180;[[ע]] + [[דֶּשֶׁא]], [[חָחִיר]] 2Ki 19:26 + Is 37:27.\r","content":"definition","show":"block"}],"notes":"","etymology":[],"morphology":[]}